title: Maldives GDP From Agriculture/ Primary Industry
description: GDP from Agriculture in Maldives decreased to 3406.50 MVR Million in 2021 from 3428.30 MVR Million in 2020. GDP from Agriculture in Maldives averaged 3045.56 MVR Million from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 3914 MVR Million in 2006 and a record low of 2298 MVR Million in 1995. This page provides - Maldives Gdp From Agriculture- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
